1.5.1

  * Proper logging messages and error handling
  
  * Decouple execution from programming and parsing 
    * Syntax tree generation from LD
    * IL Code generation from LD
    * Compile on load, execute in loop
    * Independent instruction code executor (vm)
  
  * Systematic integration test (blackbox)
  * Unit test framework (whitebox)
  * conditional JMP support
  * graceful handling of kill signals
  * timeout in microcode execution for infinite loop prevention
  * preallocated stack for stack overflow prevention
  * various bugfixes
 
